{"tid":1070740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女床戰5小時不中斷　絕頂升天變死屍","createTime":"2019-03-21T01:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T01:58:43.000Z","uid":32511,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f1992a5741693212ce8943cf3a258f21baec2917","tid":1070740,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ifHoB0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ifHoB0.jpg&h=f5ce1342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞一名32歲女子「拉菲拉」(La Fiera，意為野獸)，連續床戰5小時不間斷，最後真的絕頂升天，變成一具冰冷遺體。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，這名女子日前和男伴到賓館做愛，但女子連續床戰5小時後，向男方表示自己感到暈眩，隨後發生心臟驟停。男方立刻打電話叫救護車，但救護車表示路途遙遠，難以短時間內抵達，隨後男子用毯子把女生包裹住之後，直接搭計程車衝向瓦雷大學醫院(University Hospital of Valle)。但到院後，醫師仍無法救回女子的命，宣告女子不治身亡。<br />\n<br />\n男方事後承認，兩人為了助性、延長做愛時間，有服藥。目前警方正詳細調查女子死因<br />\n，並釐清女子是否有長期用藥的習慣。"},{"pid":"16b3cb2db063ef19e73ab93e1ad01c841008bb12","tid":1070740,"uid":9890,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:27:58.000Z","msg":"今次真係屌死人"},{"pid":"f0a76018ea5d160537ce58573448091858134295","tid":1070740,"uid":215900,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:29:29.000Z","msg":"精盡人亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1174fc25be65de1c7a9b00f9faaca65baf6266c6","tid":1070740,"uid":186529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:34:10.000Z","msg":"耕壞嘅田"},{"pid":"7d4263f7cf123603e4f4aa06ff8fbb929e691971","tid":1070740,"uid":62822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:35:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3210a262629d33742b9494ebd8ea4d2c973b880","tid":1070740,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:36:57.000Z","msg":"男嘅反而無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61048133a41e490c0e4009d4f531236fc811e2a5","tid":1070740,"uid